Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}原来在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.36,D5-Answer,,0,0,0,,梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}你们等着 蛆虫们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}只要我吃下特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}好痒 好痒 好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}用这个
